<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="maximum-scale=1.0,width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,user-scalable=0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />

    <!-- libs: jquery, bootstrap, font-awesome, lodash, backbone, mustache -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="jquery/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="http://code.jquery.com/ui/1.10.3/jquery-ui.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <script type="text/javascript" src="bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
    <script type="text/javascript" src="lodash/dist/lodash.underscore.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="backbone/backbone-min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="mustache/mustache.js"></script>

    <!-- board -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="javascripts/index.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
  <header>
    <!-- gnb: navbar -->
    <div class="gnb navbar navbar-inverse navbar-static-top" role="navigation">
      <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display -->
      <div class="navbar-header">
        <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-8">
          <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          <span class="icon-bar"></span>
        </button>
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"><i class="fa fa-clipboard"></i>&nbsp;Summerboard</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling -->
      <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-8">
        <!-- with user -->
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right" style="display:none;">
          <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-bell"></i>&nbsp;Notification</a></li>
          <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-clipboard"></i>&nbsp;Board</a></li>
          <li><img class="account img-rounded" src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/47236e140589881bbadb777a44340140.png" alt="" /></li>
        </ul>
        <!-- without user -->
        <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
          <li class="account-login dropdown">
            <a href="#" class="account-login-btn dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown">Login</a>
            <div class="account-login-dropdown dropdown-menu">
              <p class="text-center">Log in</p>
              <hr/>
              <form action="/login" method="post">
                <div class="input-group">
                  <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-user"></i></span>
                  <input name="username" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Username">
                </div>
                <div class="input-group">
                  <span class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-key"></i></span>
                  <input name="password" type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Password">
                </div>
                <input type="submit" class="btn btn-success pull-right" value="Log in">
              </form>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div><!-- /.navbar-collapse -->
    </div>
  </header>
  <div class="jumbotron text-center">
    <h1><i class="fa fa-clipboard"></i>&nbsp;Summerboard</h1>
    <h2 class="text-muted">Organize anything, together.</h2>
    <p><br/></p>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h2>Intuitive</h2>
        <p>Get organized as fast as you can think. The easy-to-use interface takes no time to learn, and every action is instantaneous, so there’s nothing standing between you and your sweet productive flow.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h2>Collborative</h2>
        <p>Summerboard is great alone, but even better with others. Get the whole group onboard in seconds. See their updates in real time. Never ask “Who’s doing what?” again.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <h2>Adapts to you</h2>
        <p>More than just a to-do list or a task manager, Summerboard is anything you want it to be—a lesson planner, a community bulletin, a repository for inspiration. We support the way you think, not the other way around.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
